description: Discover elevated city living at 502 E 3rd Street, Unit A — a striking 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath townhouse offering nearly 1,900 square feet across four beautifully designed levels, complete with a private entrance, oversized garage, and standout outdoor space. The heart of the home is an open-concept living area with a custom built-in bar, perfect for hosting or relaxing in style. A chef’s kitchen features Leicht cabinetry, stone countertops, and premium Thermador appliances—all curated by interior designer Louis Ashman and the team at Divine Design Center. Upstairs, the full-floor primary suite is your personal retreat, with custom Italian closets and a spa-inspired ensuite bath. Two additional bedrooms, a full bath, and in-unit laundry offer flexible space for guests, family, or a home office. Step outside to your private fenced-in patio—complete with a hot tub—making it a rare oasis in the heart of Southie. An extra-large heated garage offers easy parking and extra storage.
